{"tid":307802,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[人道災難] 有用PhotoBucket的你即刻上電腦backup圖片","createTime":"2017-07-03T15:36:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-19T13:01:28.000Z","uid":58729,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb45c26cadf74cb72786d9380f0bd95d17d15bb4","tid":307802,"uid":58729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ir0.mobify.com/500/http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/30/124844_c62918c58d2907d1315f447b38be3fb1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fir0.mobify.com%2F500%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F30%2F124844_c62918c58d2907d1315f447b38be3fb1.jpg&h=d5681797&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係岩岩先知, 自己用左 photobucket 好耐, 無啦啦D 相死咗link<br />\n因為我有將D 相外連 <br />\n基本上, 你所有外連嘅相都會 lock鬼咗, 要你俾錢升級會員先可以解鎖<br />\n外連即係 你有喺第三方網站展示你嘅圖片, 例如 lihkg<br />\n<br />\n有用photobucket 的你, 立即用電腦登入 photobucket , download 番你個 album<br />\n岩岩我download完 總算救到大部份嘅相 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18fa3d48e2445223660752275f11f82af46b589f","tid":307802,"uid":58729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T17:03:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12349b432a955cb087c9da03391b798d0b65b62f","tid":307802,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T19:52:19.000Z","msg":"This week's digital preservation fail"},{"pid":"317ba76c922d404492c761ecec0ef844fb1ddf07","tid":307802,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-04T04:02:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n等淘汰"},{"pid":"9b83043806b1a8725381cd5625efa3b8387cb634","tid":307802,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T20:20:16.000Z","msg":"依家冇鎖你啲相，不過要俾錢先有得外連"},{"pid":"e1912c5a7820ea25396628d3d7dcdfd2bde3d19a","tid":307802,"uid":42119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19